1314
01:26:23,274 --> 01:26:25,574
And there was
never any doubt

1315
01:26:25,576 --> 01:26:28,613
when I asked what
her greatest creation was.

1316
01:26:31,617 --> 01:26:33,217
It was you.

1317
01:26:51,836 --> 01:26:53,536
Clara.

1318
01:26:53,538 --> 01:26:56,608
Father, I'm so sorry.

1319
01:27:01,714 --> 01:27:02,881
I'm sorry.

